sources have unofficially confirmed that Amber Heard has been sacked from AM2. Apparently they don't want to start filming and then get left in the lurch if she gets hauled off to jail for falsifying evidence, a very real possibility.

What a sh*t show that's going to be, with everybody from James Franco to Elon Musk already subpoenaed to appear. People think that those two are being called because they allegedly cheated with Amber in Johnny's penthouse, but I think they're going to be asked to testify that they didn't see any marks on her in the days following her claim that she was beaten.
It's pretty obvious what was going on, but the meat of the matter is that she faked those bruises, and those two can testify to that - or risk perjuring themselves.
So, it may be a little while before we get OFFICIAL confirmation, but we can unofficially start the party.
